\id GLO - Ogea New Testament; Don Adeb, Marib F. and Auba; 12-September-2013 
\mt1 Beele kuruwei nomo beele mora  
\p \k Aron\k*: \it (Luk 1.5; Aposel 7.40; Hibru 5.4; 7.11; 9.4)\it*  
\pi1 Aron no Moses nomo bemu hiloufe, onodu no Jekop idau gane 12 waha nebereha ete, no Liwai nomo asa.  
\p \k Abel\k*: \it (Matiu 23.35; Luk 11.51; Hibru 11.4; 12.24)\it*  
\pi1 Abel no Kein bemu menekele, Adam Ive ngare idanere.  
\p \k Abraham\k*:  
\pi1 Abraham no Aisak umamu, nomo oya Sara. Onodu no Israelha fai-aita bagu olobeta mutu 12 waha nebere asanege. No Itou nomo beele oojo dewainga Itou no fai tigini tuwai.  
\p \k Adam\k*: \it (Luk 3.38; Rom 5.14; 1 Korin 15.22-45; 1 Timoti 2.13-14; Jut 14)\it*  
\pi1 Adam no fai amugou, Itou no oula langa atai. Onodu no Kein Abel ngare amenere.  
\p \k Alta\k*:  
\pi1 Alta no Itou nomo eeya muru wari fugou kabali.  
\p \k Ensel\k*:  
\pi1 Ensel nere hauri, nere Itou ngate ha laluwa langa yafa bode, Itou nomo horinga te fubode nomo fai-aita bagu oofa nigi-nigide.  
\p \k Aposel\k*:  
\pi1 Aposel nigide wa nere Yesus bode huwanyanege ngalenga wainga, no haruwe nigainga nomo beele tedu bode fai ila togoi nagane waha. Nere disaipel 12 wa nere Yesus nomo aposel.  
\p \k Beele baara tawou bogis\k*: \it (Hibru 9.4; Hbmw 11.9)\it*  
\pi1 Bogis waha nere falanga langa atane, nomo gogala oruwa gol kutauwou. Nomo huwanya langa megebu aroro nga jiridere, Itou no nuuni beele megebu nga waha langa yerege nirai \it (Hibru 9.4-5)\it*.  
\p \k Yage bisou\k*:  
\pi1 Jon no fai-aita bagu Jordan yaage lang yaage bisemu nigai. Wa ere ubuludu Itou boya huwanyage nalengana waha abitimuwou.  
\p \k Benjamin\k*: \it (Aposel 13.21; Rom 11.1; Filipai 3.5; Hbmw 7.8)\it*  
\pi1 Benjamin no Jekop nomo idau gane 12 waha nebereha ete. Onodu no Israel nebere olobeta mutu 12 waha nebereha ete.  
\p \k Kanaan\k*:  
\pi1 Kanaan wa no oula mutu ete, Itou no Israel nigei nomo bona beele baara tawai waha. Elebe oula waha unyi Israel.  
\p \k Kristen\k*: \it (Aposel 26.28; 1 Pita 4.16)\it*  
\pi1 Kristen wa fai-aita bagu huwanyanege ubuludu Yesus Kristus nomo beele oojode waha.  
\p \k Elaija\k*: \it (Matiu 11.14; Mak 9.4; Rom 11.12; Jems 5.17)\it*  
\pi1 Elaija no Itou nomo profet ete. Ariya nomo aasa Jems 5.17 langa yeregou inyina.  
\p \k Baraou\k*:  
\pi1 Barau wa nere hauri inyaba.  
\p \k Fik\k*:  
\pi1 Fik wa no nauge ete, nomo fatu wa no unyuru bagu.  
\p \k Gidion\k*: \it (Hibru 1.32)\it*  
\pi1 Gidion no Israel nebere mora bagu anyakaro ete.  
\p \k Grik\k*:  
\pi1 Grik wa no kantri ete nomo unyi. Grik nomo taon anyakaro nomo unyi Atens.  
\p \k Hauri Guuni\k*:  
\pi1 Hauri Guuni no hauri, no fai-aita bagu huwanyanege langa inyi bona, onowou hilou bona isou nigi-nigina.  
\p \k Aisak\k*: \it (Aposel 7.8; Rom 9.7; Hibru 11.9)\it*  
\pi1 Aisak no Abraham Sara ngare idanere.  
\p \k Israel\k*:  
\pi1 Israel unyi waha Itou Jekop tuwai. Kantri Jekop nomo asa gane yafade waha fere unyi Israel ide.  
\p \k Jesi\k*: \it (Matiu 1.5-6; Luk 3.22; Aposel 13.22; Rom 15.12)\it*  
\pi1 Jesi no king Davit umamu, onodu Yesus no king Davit asa.  
\p \k Yesus\k*:  
\pi1 Yesus unyi nomo hugu wa, gidu haigou fai.  
\p \k Juda\k*:  
\pi1 Nere Juda nigide wa nere Abraham nomo asa ganenga. Wa nere Israel wenga.  
\p \k Josep\k*:  
\pi1 Josep no Jekop nomo idau gane 12 waha nebereha ete.  
\pi1 Josep ete wa no Maria au. \it (Matiu 13.55; Mak 6.3)\it*  
\pi1 Josep ete fere wa Jems bemu menekele. \it (Matiu 27.56)\it*  
\pi1 Josep ete wa no Arimateaha moni fai, onodu no Juda nebere kaunsel amugou waha nebereha ete. \it (Matiu 27.57-60)\it*  
\pi1 Barabas ide wa fere nere Josep tude. \it (Aposel 4.36)\it*  
\p \k Josuwa\k*: \it (Aposel 7.45; Hibru 4.36)\it*  
\pi1 Moses umainga, iinga Josuwa no Israel nebere morabagu heigedu bona, Israel hanigainga Kenan oula langa goyane.  
\p \k Itou nomo sipsip magana\k*: \it (Jon 1.29-36)\it*  
\pi1 Jon yaage bisemu nigigou fai, no Yesus “Itou nomo sipsip magana” tuwai.  
\p \k Nuuni beele\k*:  
\pi1 Itou no nuuni beele 10 Moses tuwaiha.  
\p \k Mesaia\k*:  
\pi1 Mesaia ide wa no Yesus wenga.  
\p \k Masted\k*: \it (Matiu 13.31-32; 17.20; Mak 4.31-32; Luk 13.19)\it*  
\pi1 Masted no malu ete yaai dorofe nomo fatu gai mene-mene.  
\p \k Prist\k*:  
\pi1 Prist nigide wa, nere nagenga fai-aita bagu nebere haumu tedu alta langa Itou eeya muuru wari fuwei nomo bode, tempel nomo jauli guuni huwanya langa goi-goide.  
\p \k Sabat\k*:  
\pi1 Wa Juda nebere bori fati guuni.  
\p \k Sadyusi\k*:  
\pi1 Wa nere Juda wenga, nere fai unyinege aroro bagu waha nere komowou hugu ete nere Juda gamanege langa heigemudu bode, Itou Moses nuuni beele tuwai waha bagu, Juda nebere fanyinege bagu tigini oojowei nomo fai-aita bagu isisiwou nigi gane.  
\p \k Samaria\k*:  
\pi1 Wa no ha mutu ete unyi. Nere fai fereha, nere Judaha uwa nere walanga yafa-yafade.  
\p \k Solomon\k*: \it (Matiu 1.6-7; 6.29; 12.42; Luk 11.31; 12.27)\it*  
\pi1 Solomon no king Devit idau. Saini umamu umainga, no Israel nebere morabagu anyakaro yafai.  
\p \k Fai nomo idau\k*:  
\pi1 Unyi beha Yesus bona lena.  
\p \k Salpa\k*: \it (Hbmw 9.17)\it*  
\pi1 Salpa waha nere sain ila lede brim megebu. No nomo urou wa dada laluwa bailu bagu dorofe, onodu nomo lalawou anyakaro onodu agiya danga bagu. Nere Itou ganya nomo paura waha langa ati-atide.  
\p \k Tempel\k*:  
\pi1 Itou eeya muru wari fugou mata.  
\p \k Topas\k*:  
\pi1 No megebu ete gai hilobainga tigini.  
\p \k Saion\k*:  
\pi1 Jerusalem taon no Saion muuju langa inyina.  